<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;6819" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6819;PEdg104</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀρτεμίδωρος Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαι, εὖ ἂν ἔχοι· ἔρρωμαι δὲ καὶ ἐγὼ καὶ Ἀπολλώνιος 

    <lb n="2"/>ὑγίαινεν καὶ τὰ <choice><corr>ἄλλα</corr><sic>ταλλ</sic></choice> ἦν κατὰ γνώμην. τοῖς Λεπτίνου υἱοῖς Νικάνδρωι καὶ Μυρικῶντι 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> Φαρβαίθωι ἵππος ἐστὶν μέλας, παραπρήματα μεγάλα ἔχων καὶ ἐπ᾽ οὐθὲν ἄλλο χρήσιμος ὢν 

    <lb n="4"/>ἔξω εἰς ὀχείαν. πυνθάνομαι δέ σοι γνωρίμους εἶναι τοὺς νεανίσκους ἐπὶ πλέον. καλῶς ἂν οὖν 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>ποιήσαις</corr><sic>ποησαις</sic></choice> μάλιστα μὲν ἀγοράσας μοι παρ᾽ αὐτῶν τὸν ἵππο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> εἰς ὀχείαν, ἐὰν ἦι μικροῦ τινος 

    <lb n="6"/>λαβεῖν· εἰ δὲ μή ἐστιν πώλιμος, χρήσαιμαι αὐτὸν εἰς τὴν <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ἐπιοῦσαν</del> ὀχείαν· <add place="supralinear">ἐὰν γὰρ σπουδάσηις, οὐ μή σοι ἀντείπωσιν·</add> <choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> πάσηι δὲ ἐπι-

    <lb n="7"/>μελείαι ἔσται. ὁποτέρως δ᾽ ἂν οἰκονομήσηις, χαριεῖ μοι γράψας τὴν ταχίστην, ἵνα εἰδῶ εἰ 

    <lb n="8"/>ὑπάρχει μοι. <add place="supralinear">ὁ γὰρ παρ᾽ ἐμοὶ ἵππος πρεσβύτερος ἤδη ὢν οὐ 

κατακρατεῖ τὰς θηλείας.</add> <choice><corr>ἐπέστειλα</corr><sic>επε<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ι</del>στειλα</sic></choice> δέ σοι καὶ περὶ τοῦ σησάμου τοῦ ἐμοι γεγονότος ἐν τῶι κλήρωι, 

    <lb n="9"/>ἵνα περί τε τῆς συγκομιδῆς σπουδάσηις, ὅπως συγκομισθῆι τρόπωι τινί, καὶ ἐμοὶ γράψηις 

    <lb n="10"/>πόσον γέγονεν. καὶ περὶ τούτων <choice><corr>οὖν</corr><sic>ουμ</sic></choice> μοι ἐπιστείλας καλῶς ἂν <choice><corr>ποιήσαις</corr><sic>ποησαις</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num>, Ἀπελλαίου <num value="5">ε</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="12"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num>. Ἀρτεμίδωρος 

    <lb n="13"/>εἰς Φιλαδέλφειαν. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἰατρός. 

    <lb n="13"/>Ζήνωνι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-253" notBefore="-253" type="textDate" value="-0253-01-25">25. Jan. 253 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59225</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">870</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59225</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;2;59225" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">SB III 6819</bibl></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">C.C. Edgar, ASAE 24, 1924, S. 37</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.870" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="figure"><p><figure hr